          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Temporary price data. Calculated as 90% of purchasers price based on: Source: 28 August 2006 issue of Chemical Market Reporter (ICIS) in USD/gal (conversion 3.7854 litre/gal; density 0.77 kg/litre). For comparison, UN Commodity Trade Statistics Database (http://data.un.org/Explorer.aspxDatabase [Accessed 2 July 2010]) has import and export prices (total trades (USD) divided by total weight (kg) in EU27, USA, China, Japan and India) for 'Cyclohexane' resulting in a price of 0.88 USD/kg.</comment>
